Changes log for Text-Demoroniser
================================

0.07    2015-01-20
        - fixed license fields in META.json to be lists.
        - extended META test suite.
        - added cpanminus to INSTALL instructions.

0.06    2013-02-03
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - updated test suite.

0.05    2012-04-22
        - META tests no longer require specific versions.
        - further spelling fix. (thanks to Florian Schlichting).

0.04    2012-04-16
        - added use warnings.
        - spelling fix. (thanks to Florian Schlichting & Gregor Herrmann).
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).

0.03    2012-04-15
        - License updated to Artistic License v2.0.
        - removed Artistic file.
        - added META.json and test script.
        - added simple example script.
        - remove DSLIP info, as its no longer used.

0.02    2010-03-02
        - implemented a better regex lookup (patched thanks to Yanick Champoux)

0.01    2009-08-11
        - Initial release.
        - originally inspired by the demoroniser script
